AI Bot backend task

Purpose:
- own event-time and post-event workflows
- scan and validate attendee QR codes
- collect feedback
- track incidents and live attendance

Suggested folder layout:
```text
aibot_event management/
  app/
  api/
  domain/
  db/
  realtime/
  tests/
```

Core responsibilities:
- QR scan intake
- check-in orchestration
- duplicate / invalid token handling
- live attendee assistance
- feedback capture
- incident logging
- operational summaries

Primary data owned by the bot:
- devices
- scan sessions
- check-ins
- bot messages
- feedback surveys
- feedback responses
- event incidents
- audit logs

External contract:
- validate tokens through Luma
- write check-ins back to Luma
- receive registration and ticket events from Luma
